creator: SPRINGMARU
descriptionHtml:
Have fun doing exciting Fix shape.
It's the pentomino style game that fill up a big box with small blocks.
You can a drag small block in a big box.
You may have to rotate the small block to fill up the box.
As you get the higher level, you will meet more difficult shape of blocks.
Your brain will be happy.


[How to play]


After the appearance of a small hand touch is moved to the desired location without lifting.
To rotate the shape slightly smaller shape by hand once a small click.
The gray in the middle of the screen with the appearance of a large fill a small form is complete, proceed to the next level.
You can see a hint after a little time.


SPRINGMARU
